パッケージ io.github.townyadvanced.flagwar.objects

クラス Cell

java.lang.Object
io.github.townyadvanced.flagwar.objects.Cell
直系の既知のサブクラス:
CellUnderAttack
public class Cell extends Object
Representation of a Towny plot, based on it's Coord, used for manipulation in FlagWar.

  • コンストラクタの詳細

    • Cell

      public Cell(String worldName, int x, int z)
      Constructs the Cell for a given WorldName, and x/z coordinates.

      See parse(String, int, int) for an example at implementation.

      パラメータ:
      worldName - Name of the world to which the cell should be associated with.
      x - The 'longitudinal' (x) value, in terms of the Towny coordinates.
      z - The 'latitudinal' (z) value, in terms of the Towny coordinates.

    • Cell

      public Cell(Cell cell)
      Constructs the Cell based on a supplied Cell (or CellUnderAttack).
      パラメータ:
      cell - the supplied Cell to clone.

    • Cell

      public Cell(org.bukkit.Location location)
      Constructs the Cell based on a supplied Location. Runs through parse(Location).
      パラメータ:
      location - the Location of the Cell.

    • parse

      public static Cell parse(String worldName, int x, int z)
      Parse raw xVal and zVal, as well as the world name to construct a new Cell.
      パラメータ:
      worldName - the name of the World the cell is found in.
      x - the base x value of the cell.
      z - the base z value of the cell.
      戻り値:
      a new Cell for the given world name, with x and z values adjusted for the appropriate Cell Size (Coord.getCellSize()).

    • parse

      public static Cell parse(com.palmergames.bukkit.towny.object.WorldCoord worldCoord)
      Parse a Towny WorldCoord into a Cell.
      パラメータ:
      worldCoord - the WorldCoord.
      戻り値:
      a new Cell from the given WorldCoord.

    • parse

      Gets the World from the supplied Location.
      パラメータ:

      戻り値:
      sends the WorldInfo.getName() and coordinates through parse(String, int, int)
